# Contribution guidelines

## Requirements
* All code must be optimized for small linux computers and the Raspberry Pi Pico 2
* Varibale names must follow the python naming convention or atleast make it understandable from a mile away
* DO NOT FORK THIS REPO unless its for contributing to this project then just press the fork button and when contributing on a fork press the contribute button.
* Please create a branch by going to the braches and making one and also make a pull request that is un-finished
* To make a Pull request press the pull requets button and new pull request. Then using the branch you created use it has its compare. Also pls add tags, name, and a description.
